               ▪ unto Christ our Thankfull remembrance of his great benefit▪ unto Men our Repentance, our Consent in doctrine, and our earnest studie and desire after Love and Charitie.
            
            66 But that this mystery is either a Propitiatorie, or Impetratorie Sacrifice, this we utterly deny.
            67 For there is but one Priest of the New Testament, one Propitiatorie
               
sacrifice, one oblation.
            
